    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride that won't break the bank? This car is a fantastic opportunity for someone who values functionality and character! It\u2019s in fair condition, showing some honest wear and tear from its years of service, but it remains a solid, drivable vehicle with plenty of life left. With a bit of continued care, this is the perfect budget-friendly choice for your daily commute!",
