    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in pristine, showroom condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied it from day one, keeping it garage-kept and meticulously detailed. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a new home, this is the one. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
