    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen a day of inclement weather. The exterior finish is flawless, featuring a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely no swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings; it has been protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating since day one. Inside, the cabin is an oasis of perfection. The premium leather upholstery remains supple and tight, free of any creasing or wear, and the original floor mats are pristine. All interior electronics, from the high-fidelity sound system to the ambient lighting, function exactly as intended. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach. It comes with a complete, documented service history from certified master technicians, using only genuine OEM parts for every scheduled maintenance interval. The engine bay is spotless, and the undercarriage remains in showroom condition. For the buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this is a rare opportunity to acquire a turn-key masterpiece.",
      "price": 44500.0,
